# Agent Detector

**Type:** Auto-Invoke (HIGHEST PRIORITY)
**Trigger:** Every message, no exceptions

## Purpose

Automatically detects which specialized agent should handle each request using a sophisticated multi-layer scoring system. This ensures every task is handled by the most appropriate expert agent.

## Activation Logic

This skill ALWAYS runs FIRST before any other skill or action. It is mandatory for every user message to determine the correct agent(s) to handle the request.

